      <title>美国银行称印度消费转型将损害小型股</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/india-s-consumption-pivot-to-hurt-smaller-stocks-bofa-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国银行策略师表示，由于印度政府缩减支出，转而采取减税措施以刺激消费，2025 年印度中小型股可能出现三年来首次下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/india-s-consumption-pivot-to-hurt-smaller-stocks-bofa-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Feb 2025 08:10:41 GMT</pubDate>
