    <item>
      <title>雀巢通过价格和品牌投资推动销售增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/nestle-sales-growth-exceeds-estimates-helped-by-higher-prices</link>
      <description><![CDATA[去年最后一个季度，雀巢公司销售额增长从历史低位回升，原因是这家全球最大的食品制造商提高了产品价格并加大了品牌投资。公司股价飙升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/nestle-sales-growth-exceeds-estimates-helped-by-higher-prices</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Feb 2025 06:24:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>外资持股比例上限取消，快乐蜂股价自 2020 年以来涨幅最大</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/jollibee-shares-jump-after-foreign-ownership-limit-scrapped</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾最大的餐饮运营商快乐蜂食品公司 (Jollibee Foods Corp.) 的股价周四出现近五年来的最大涨幅，此前该公司获得证券交易所的批准，取消了 40% 的外资持股比例限制。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/jollibee-shares-jump-after-foreign-ownership-limit-scrapped</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Feb 2025 03:16:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
